001package imagingbook.calibration.data.zhang;
002
003import imagingbook.core.resource.ImageResource;
004
005public enum CalibrationImage implements ImageResource {
006                CalibIm1_png("CalibIm1.png"),
007                CalibIm2_png("CalibIm2.png"),
008                CalibIm3_png("CalibIm3.png"),
009                CalibIm4_png("CalibIm4.png"),
010                CalibIm5_png("CalibIm5.png"),
011                marked1_png("marked1.png"),
012                marked2_png("marked2.png"),
013                marked3_png("marked3.png"),
014                marked4_png("marked4.png"),
015                marked5_png("marked5.png"),
016                CalibImageStack_tif("CalibImageStack.tif");
017
018        private final static String BASEDIR = "DATA";
019        private final String filename;
020        
021        CalibrationImage(String filename) {
022                this.filename = filename;
023        }
024        
025        @Override
026        public String getFileName() {
027                return filename;
028        }
029        
030        @Override
031        public String getRelativeDirectory() {
032                return BASEDIR;
033        }
034        
035        
036        public static void main(String[] args) {
037                for (ImageResource ir : CalibrationImage.values()) {
038                        System.out.println(ir.getImage().toString());
039                }
040        }
041
042}
